  <li><a href="http://yaakaito.github.com/contact">Contact</a></li>
</ul>
</nav>

</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nt">&lt;/header&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>こんな感じにして、</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><h1><a href="http://yaakaito.github.com/"><span>yaakaito github bloh</span></a></h1>

</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;nav</span> <span class="na">role=</span><span class="s">&quot;navigation&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>\{\% include custom/navigation.html \%\}<span class="nt">&lt;/nav&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>さらにこんな感じにする、headerとかnavigationの内容はちょいちょいかわりそうなので<code>custom</code>以下にあるのが良さそうですね。</p>
]]></content>
